{"tid":273962,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"學普通話 考名校有著數","createTime":"2017-06-07T03:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T05:28:28.000Z","uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe306bb5476d481d92c5f1415a6a9d1875def4bc","tid":273962,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:21:42.000Z","msg":"以前想考名校，說得一口流利英語有數，但近年普通話有後來居上之勢，如港島名校聖保羅男女中學，自去年起便已在招收中一新生時測試普通話能力，明年在中一班更以普通話授中文科，可知講普通話已是不可改變的大潮流。想仔女上課時更易聽得明白，便要從小加強培訓，學好普通話。"},{"pid":"1da9cb97528620eb462e0f1035e868f0d6b036df","tid":273962,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:29:48.000Z","msg":"有屎你仲唔食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808eddf0c1aaafc0e5c3d34a9a8109cfe2dd2b65","tid":273962,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有屎你仲唔食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n甬把屎尿掛在嘴邊啦"},{"pid":"ef2c85bfd8bb0ade2e9125c9173bafa728ae60f9","tid":273962,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"因為ff國際語言"}]}